    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it does show its age. Mechanically, the car starts and runs consistently, but it may require some minor suspension work and a tune-up in the near future to address occasional rough idling. The exterior has several noticeable scratches and a small dent on the rear passenger door, while the interior shows significant wear on the driver's seat and some fading on the dashboard plastics. All major systems like the heater and lights are functional, making this a solid choice for someone looking for an affordable, functional vehicle who doesn't mind a bit of cosmetic and mechanical character.",
