    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle represents a premier opportunity for the discerning driver. Featuring a robust powertrain and a well-appointed interior, this model offers a balanced synthesis of performance and everyday utility. Thoroughly inspected to ensure mechanical integrity, it stands as a testament to enduring engineering. Experience a sophisticated driving dynamic at an exceptional value.",
      "price": 31500.0,
