    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm looking to find a new home for my trusty car. It's been a fantastic ride and is still in really solid shape\u2014super clean inside and runs like a charm! I've taken great care of it, so it's totally ready for your next road trip or just the daily commute. It's a reliable beauty that still has so much life left in it. Feel free to reach out if you want to come by and take it for a spin!",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 20
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically robust 2008 BMW M3 (E92) featuring the high-revving S65 4.0L V8 engine. This atmospheric powerplant utilizes eight individual throttle bodies and a 12.0:1 compression ratio to deliver linear power up to an 8,400 RPM redline. The drivetrain is anchored by a 6-speed manual transmission and a GKN ViscoLok M-Variable differential. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including rod bearing replacement and throttle actuator service. The chassis remains composed with Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and updated bushings, ensuring the MacPherson strut/multi-link suspension geometry performs as intended. While the paint exhibits minor road-rash consistent with its mileage, the structural integrity and powertrain harmonics are excellent. A true driver\u2019s specification optimized for thermal efficiency and corner-exit traction.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 20
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Mechanically sound. Clean interior. Recently serviced. Title in hand.",
      "price": 29500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 20
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a prime example of pride in ownership, offering a seamless blend of performance and comfort. The exterior maintains a lustrous finish, showing only the minor, inevitable road wear of a well-traveled car, with no significant scratches or dings to speak of. Inside, the cabin is remarkably clean and has been kept in a smoke-free environment; the leather upholstery is supple with minimal bolstering wear, and the dashboard remains free of any sun damage. Every feature, from the responsive touchscreen interface to the heated seats and dual-zone climate control, operates perfectly. Mechanically, the car is in robust health, having undergone a comprehensive multi-point inspection and a recent oil service. The engine pulls smoothly, the transmission shifts are crisp, and the suspension provides a quiet, composed ride. It comes with a complete set of floor mats, two keys, and a documented service history that underscores its reliability. This is a dependable, high-quality vehicle ready for immediate use.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 20
    },
    {
